<p>View the <a href="https://github.com/jas0nmjames/jas0nmjames.github.io/commits/master">commit history</a> to see how development progressed over time.</p>

<p>If you have any questions about why Iâ€™m using html classes and ids the way I am, or how Iâ€™m using liquid templating, or other choices I made, please let me know!</p>

